Detailed Description

template<class T_KEY, class T_ITEM, class U_POOL, class U_KEY = AkGetArrayKey< T_KEY, T_ITEM >, unsigned long TGrowBy = 1>
class AkSortedKeyArray< T_KEY, T_ITEM, U_POOL, U_KEY, TGrowBy >

Array of items, sorted by key. Uses binary search for lookups. BEWARE WHEN MODIFYING THE ARRAY USING BASE CLASS METHODS.
